<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">The rules are pretty simple.
<br />

<br />
1. Maintain a mature attitude while you're here. Different points of view are bound to happen. That's actually a good thing! Some times you will just have to agree to disagree. Resorting to immature behavior is not acceptable. 
<br />

<br />
2. Trolls will not be fed here. If you are trolling you will be banned from the site. The mods and myself take a hard line on this. I have seen too many excellent sites go down the tubes to bullies and trolls. And the people here have worked very hard to make this board what it is. 
<br />

<br />
3. No name calling, no insulting, no excessive whinning ... you get the idea. See rules #1 and #2.  This site has been free from the usual BS you see on other sites. That's what makes us so different and enjoyable.
<br />

<br />
4. <span style="font-weight: bold">No</span> Politics, period.
<br />

<br />

<br />
 Pretty simple. This is the one area where I will take a hard stance. The integrity of the site WILL be preserved.</span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Juwel on Fri Jan 28, 2005 6:48 am; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
</td></tr>
